  <h2>Federation / school resources</h2>
  <p>Placeholder for official school or federation materials that should be summarized and cited rather than copied.</p>
  <h2>Online references</h2>
  <p>Placeholder for reputable online references with access dates and concise summaries.</p>
  <h2>Video references</h2>
  <p>Placeholder for video notes, timestamps, and attribution where permitted.</p>
  <h2>Notes on copyright and attribution</h2>
  <p class="callout">Do not copy copyrighted curriculum text or images directly. Summarize, cite, and use original photos, notes, diagrams, or public-domain / licensed assets when possible.</p>
</ContentLayout>
